    <text type="note" xml:lang="ru" xml:id="letter-09082"> 
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <date when-custom="1788-08-26">1788 г. августа 26.</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>Сие письмо, <date when-custom="1788-08-26">сего дня</date> полученное, пошлите казать <rs ref="people.xml#ost05">вице-канцлеру</rs>
                <note type="editorial">
                    Catherine writes about her letter to <persName ref="people.xml#spr01">baron Georg Magnus Sprengtporten</persName>, in which she talks about the intention to separate Swedish and Finnish armies and let Sprengtporten command the Finns. A.V. Khrapovitskii noted in his diary under <date when-custom="1788-08-26">the same day</date> that he showed this letter to <rs ref="people.xml#ost05">Vice-Chancellor</rs> as he was ordered (
                    <bibl>
                        <title ref="works.xml#dnevni02">Dnevnik A.V. Khrapovitskago s 18 ianvaria 1782 po 17 sentiabria 1793 goda</title>
                        , <biblScope unit="pp">pp. 80.</biblScope>
                    </bibl>
                    ).
                </note>. Я думаю писать к <persName ref="people.xml#mus02">Пушкину</persName>, чтоб <rs ref="people.xml#mus02">он</rs> <placeName ref="places.xml#swe01">Шведам</placeName> и <placeName ref="places.xml#fin01">Финнам</placeName> дал выразуметь, что как <placeName ref="places.xml#den01">Датчане</placeName> войну <rs ref="places.xml#swe01 places.xml#fin01">им</rs> объявили, то уже о мире и перемирии теперь не время говорить, разве <placeName ref="places.xml#fin01">Финны</placeName> отстанут от <placeName ref="places.xml#swe01">Шведов</placeName>.</p>
        </body>
